XML-FuncWriter version 0.01
===========================

Easy XML Writing.

This module is still a work in progress.

Documentation is in the works.  See the tests for usage.  See design_notes.txt for the, well, design.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.pl
   build
   build test
   build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires no other libraries:

